text: They used to be good...but now just terrible. Second time, I have a dish swimming in oil. First time, let it go. Now the second time? Also, the lady taking the order can't speak a word of English!!! Everything I point at first...she shake her head. At least the boss came or no order...shake my head.

I ordered the Pao Fan (rice in soup) for takeaway and they mixed in the rice and fried grains into the soup in a single container. By the time I got home, the rice and fried grains were already soggy. No quality of service. And the guy was rude when I complaint abt it on the spot.
They changed owners and the food is better now. Good service too. Friendly environment!
Delicious Salted Egg Prawn Balls üëç so far the food we have had from here are very good. Will definitely go back for more.
Ordered a few dishes and actually the food is quite disappointing. Won't be going back again.
